---
title: Claude Uplift Flow
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> LoadSession: load_session
    LoadSession --> Navigate: Round 1
    LoadSession --> ReuseTab: Round 2+
    Navigate --> CheckAuth
    ReuseTab --> CheckAuth
    CheckAuth --> ComposeUplift: Round 1
    CheckAuth --> InjectReview: Round 2+ (skills already loaded)
    ComposeUplift --> InjectUplift: inbox/skills/* + template + persona
    InjectUplift --> SendUplift: .ProseMirror + base64_chunked_insert
    SendUplift --> WaitAck: [data-is-streaming] gone
    WaitAck --> InjectReview: Claude acknowledges skills
    InjectReview --> SendReview: base64_chunked_insert
    SendReview --> WaitResponse: wait_for_stable (3min max)
    WaitResponse --> Extract: [data-testid='chat-message-content']
    Extract --> SaveOutbox: outbox/responses/
    SaveOutbox --> HashEvidence: SHA-256 chain
    HashEvidence --> ReturnResult: {status, scores, page_id}
    ReturnResult --> [*]

    note right of ComposeUplift
        Claude.ai cannot browse URLs.
        ALL content must be injected as text.
        Uplift injection is MORE critical here.
    end note
